org.jsapar.model

Class EmptyCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jsapar.model.Cell<String>
      • org.jsapar.model.EmptyCell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class EmptyCell
extends Cell<String>
    This class is a special case where an empty value has been parsed from a source. It can be used as a type independent placeholder of an empty value.
    See Also:
